creator: Federal Authority for Identity & Citizenship
descriptionHtml:
This application allows locals, residents, and visitors of the United Arab Emirates to benefit from the services of the Federal Authority for Identity and Citizenship like visas, residencies, payment of fines, printing the family book, renewal of passport for the citizens and many other services.
Summary of the services:
Apply for a residence entry permit for your family members. Apply for new residence for your family members. Renew residence permits for your family members Apply for cancelling resident for any sponsored under your sponsorship Apply for a visit visa for your relatives You can generate the “travel status report” and the list of people you sponsor (“sponsor and sponsored report”). Check your residence and entry permit status Request a new or renew your UAE passport Print the family book for locals Extend your on arrival visa Pay fines of visas and residencies
descriptionShort: Immigration and Citizenship Services of the Federal Authority for Identity.
